      "type": "ValidationResult",
      "name": "Nominal operating point experiment 1 — hemolysis index comparison",
      "description": "CFD-predicted relative hemolysis index compared against in-vitro measurement at the nominal operating point (flow rate 5 L/min, rotational speed 3000 RPM). Predicted RH = 0.81; measured RH = 0.84; relative error 3.6%. Three replicate experiments were conducted at this single operating point. All three replicates yielded CFD-to-experiment agreement within 5%, confirming acceptable model accuracy at the nominal condition."
    },
    {
      "id": "https://uofa.net/synth/validation/morrison-vr-nominal-exp2",
